"title": "6023: sin, universality of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6023",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>All human beings sin and are guilty in the sight of God on account of an inherently sinful disposition, which can be traced back to Adam. Acts of sin thus arise from a sinful human heart. The basis of cleansing and cancellation of “original sin” is the atoning death of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Adam, the cause of universal sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:19\">ROM 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:24\">GEN 3:1–3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:22\">1CO 15:22</a></p>\n<h2>The universe is in subjection to sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:22\">GAL 3:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:21\">ROM 5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:32\">ROM 11:32</a></p>\n<h2>Sin is inherent in human nature</h2>\n<h3>Sinfulness from birth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:5\">PSA 51:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job25:4\">JOB 25:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:3\">PSA 58:3</a></p>\n<h3>The sinful heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5\">GEN 6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:21\">GEN 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:3\">ECC 9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:9\">JER 17:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19\">MAT 15:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21\">MRK 7:21</a></p>\n<h3>The sinful nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:3\">EPH 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:6-Rom8:8\">ROM 8:6–8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:19-Gal5:21\">GAL 5:19–5:21</a></p>\n<h2>The universality of sin</h2>\n<h3>No-one is righteous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:9-Rom3:19\">ROM 3:9–3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:9\">PSA 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:7\">PSA 10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:1-Ps14:3\">PSA 14:1–14:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps53:1-Ps53:3\">PSA 53:1–53:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:1\">PSA 36:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:3\">PSA 140:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:7-Isa59:8\">ISA 59:7–59:8</a></p>\n<h3>All have sinned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23\">ROM 3:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:11-Gen6:12\">GEN 6:11–6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:46\">1KI 8:46</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:36\">2CH 6:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:20\">ECC 7:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:6\">ISA 53:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:32\">ROM 1:18–1:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:2\">JAS 3:2</a></p>\n<h3>Everyone is sinful in God's sight</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:8\">1JN 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:3\">PSA 130:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:2\">PSA 143:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:9\">PRO 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:6-Isa64:7\">ISA 64:6–64:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:17\">MAT 19:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:18\">MRK 10:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:19\">LUK 18:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:10\">1JN 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>Some characters in Scripture are described as being blameless in comparison with their contemporaries</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:24\">GEN 5:24</a> <em>Enoch</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:9\">GEN 6:9</a> <em>Noah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:5\">1KI 15:5</a> <em>David</em></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ alone is sinless</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:22\">1PE 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:9\">ISA 53:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:47\">LUK 23:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:21\">2CO 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:26\">HEB 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:5\">1JN 3:5</a></p>",
